# AI-Solutions Website System

## Project Overview

The AI-Solutions Website System is a responsive web application developed as part of the **CET333 Product Development** module at the **University of Sunderland**. The project was developed using the Waterfall Software Development Methodology and provides an online platform for showcasing AI-powered software development services.

The website enables visitors to explore company information, services, projects, blogs, events, testimonials, and gallery content while allowing administrators to manage website content through a secure administration panel. An AI-powered chatbot has also been integrated to provide automated customer support.

