## Installation Guide

### Step 1

Clone the repository.

```
git clone https://github.com/susankhadka1234/ai-chatbot-solutions.git
```

### Step 2

Move the project folder into the **htdocs** directory of XAMPP.

Example:

```
C:\xampp\htdocs\ai-chatbot-solutions
```

### Step 3

Create a PostgreSQL database.

Database Name

```
ai_solutions
```

### Step 4

Import the SQL database.

```
database/ai_solutions.sql
```

### Step 5

Configure the database connection inside:

```
config/database.php
```

Example:

```php
$host = "localhost";
$dbname = "ai_solutions";
$user = "postgres";
$password = "SUsan@12#$%";
```

### Step 6

Start Apache from XAMPP.

### Step 7

Open your browser.

```
http://localhost/ai-chatbot-solutions/
```

