## AI Chatbot

The website includes an AI-powered chatbot developed using the Google Gemini API.

The chatbot provides responses related to:

- Company Information
- Services
- Projects
- Blogs
- Events
- Gallery
- Testimonials
- Feedback
- Contact Details
- Website Development
- Software Development
- AI Chatbots
- Business Automation

